                <div>
                    <h3>MINJUKIM SS22 BARI</h3>
                    <p>
                        The concept of MINJUKIM's collection is "BARI".<br>
                        "BARI" is the one and only god among many gods,<br>
                        praying to people by coming and going between <br> 
                        the underworld and this world.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <a href="/store">
                    <button class="btn3 btn-tp3">
